                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300"><i data-lucide="ticket" class="w-4 h-4 text-gold"></i><span>Voucher Diskon Saya</span></div>
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-zinc-300"></i>
